check                   Check an R package on R-hub
check_for_cran          Check an R-package on R-hub, for a CRAN
                        submission
check_on_linux          Check an R package on an R-hub platform
get_check               Retrieve the result of R-hub checks
last_check              The last rhub check of this R session
list_my_checks          List all checks for an email address
list_package_checks     List checks of a package
list_validated_emails   List validated email addresses
local_check_linux       Run a package check locally, in a Docker
                        container
local_check_linux_images
                        List R-hub Docker images
platforms               List all R-hub platforms
rhub-ids                R-hub check ids
rhub_check              An 'rhub_check' object holds status and results
                        of rhub checks
validate_email          Validate an email address on R-hub
